    "en": {
      "title": "Mother jumping into river with children; The boy is killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 32-year-old mother with her two children jumped into the Chandrika river in Mpilipitiya.",
        "While the 5-year-old boy died, the said mother and her 11-year-old son were rescued by the Sri Lanka Police Lifesaving Unit.",
        "The mother has been admitted to the intensive care unit. Investigations are underway into the incident. (R)"
      ],
